Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能打開試卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了拜託了拜託了拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艱苦的考試也只剩下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試一結束就將迎來盼望已久的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  這東西真的很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才250日圓好便宜  實在是太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:28.37,biaoti6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}桂糖甜甜圈·幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你這麼轉就能轉出好成績的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰會拼命讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說可不對哦  小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這支鉛筆可是用靈山富士山上的稀有樹木做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的人跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Made in China
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你倒是早點注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中國  也有富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能光靠瞎蒙或是求神拜佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不踏踏實實努力一下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看來是要熬通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這情況該怎麼形容你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡人事  聽天命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你會盡人事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考試其實也不算甚麼  在暑假前的這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的準備工作正在有條不紊地進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密手冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美的點子引起了大家的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  這個網頁就是小芽的力作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把數據輸入這張表格馬上就能反映在網頁上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能實時閱覽到學園祭的運行情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽是個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時也就這樣了  要是有甚麼意見儘管跟我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}San Diego{\r}\N聖地牙哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　Gorilla{\r}\NGo  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喇  喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Pants{\r}\N內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網頁不斷地被加以改良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人名義也能參展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冊子上寫著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但該做些甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上甚麼都行  只要在預算範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校方面進行審查的3天內可以隨意嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨意嘗試？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我已經先提交了申請書啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假結束後還有一次最終確認日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要參展  你可以做最終選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也來申請看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備的50本小冊子  很快就分發完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後不得不慌慌張張地連夜趕做新的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來進行的比較順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會的同學們都很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我話先說在這裡哦  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的計劃或者是不符合學生本分的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不會批准的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有過歌劇樂團的前車之鑒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭可是長期以來一直延續至今的傳統大會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒有說讓它正式中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做與不做之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能很大程度地影響著學園祭的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…不過…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們都十分罕見地積極…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著那番景象…呃…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就儘量朝積極的方面去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按這些相連且一樣的圖案…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超過一定的分數就能得到點數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過使用這些點數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在學園祭網站上  購買一些特別的虛擬形象之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  那些具體創意的構思就交給你們了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:51.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們最終是要  讓大家都能在自己的PDA上進行遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（PDA=Personal Digital Assistant  就是學美她們腰上帶著的那個…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在向外界公開之前要進行充分的試玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  明天的考試沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵奮戰考試吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽  你很怕熱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感覺是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:28.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（壘球縣大會）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候  買冰棒吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊賣的冰棒  我都還沒中過獎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（壘球縣大會）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱的話在屋裡吃冰棒不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在熱天底下吃冰棒  才能體會到夏季的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個秘密期待禮卷究竟是甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集起來就會有好事情發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是學美嘛  好像她也沒有考慮甚麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  壘球部的縣大賽最後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也盡人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝敗乃兵家常事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（未中獎）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我早些注意到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（聖櫻學園壘球部  縣大賽  決定最終勝負的慘痛失誤）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:41.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得對於新生來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對社團招新然後一擁而上似乎是一種慣例呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國中的時候大家都是怎麼叫你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那我也可以叫你蜜柑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我小睦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  上原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼叫我的話  我是不會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在櫻花飛舞時相遇的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有被雨聲所抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…考前復習？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…無論甚麼時候看起來都是這麼厲害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我馬上把他們趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  最近過得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不准直接叫名字  不然我殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  睦月你稍微注意一下腳邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收拾一下不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是我放在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰放的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  別把果汁打翻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙巾  拿紙巾來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你開甚麼電視啊  我要開始復習了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你復習你的有甚麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼關係…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  光香  這裡會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說了不要直接叫名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  借給你玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的  你們在幹甚麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了  不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倒是聽我說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說在客人的面前你們就不覺得丟臉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟臉的是姐姐你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我要小便…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忍著！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒事的  我沒在意啦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想這麼熱鬧就不會覺得寂寞了  我覺得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於明天考試的範圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是考試的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你教教她了  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼教不教的  蜜柑你的智能水平和我差不多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來比一比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們休息一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我們真是勇者啊  是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在期末考試前一天晚上\N甩著手來吃甜甜圈喝牛奶咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  關於學園祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不要說學園祭的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦  那我們聊聊棒球吧  棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要說棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…就聊格鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼職業摔跤怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和格鬥是一樣的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則太複雜了  我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的興趣都不一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會成為朋友呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了？  也不開燈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成一個人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著勸還在的幾個人加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得學生會很不錯的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這樣算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去勸勸看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會弄濕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能打開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了拜託了拜託了拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一門考試也完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假前的學生會業務就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是結束了也不能太放鬆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期間每週集合一次  進行定期的學園祭準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我提議召開慰勞會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是聽我說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是來自下島的特別募捐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且車站前的Miss Donut牛奶咖啡可以無限續杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆我們去那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Donut稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我  非常快樂
